{"tid":39763,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"隔離post話周杰倫創作能力高過家駒「好多班」","createTime":"2016-12-14T18:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T06:23:23.000Z","uid":27210,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"37e390019eb9b5f75c5d7215889a7425e2fc1f5f","tid":39763,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T18:18:30.000Z","msg":"利申先 我兩個都鍾意<br />\n事緣我拋低一句話<span style=\"color: red;\">我覺得</span>華人樂壇最有才華係佢兩個<br />\n點知俾人覆句咁嘅嘢，仲有人和應<br />\n<br />\n唔係話要爭論乜<br />\n但估唔到過咗咁多年我哋香港人都係唔識得欣賞家駒，更加唔好講其他本地創作人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好擔心之後仲會唔會有人識/欣賞佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db2069b35b4bd45e39d32de273cf29ab9bfeafb","tid":39763,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T18:23:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33598dc671c9492ba435756296ccfb6ab3dccd5","tid":39763,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T18:25:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i4/kabOg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi4%2FkabOg.jpg&h=321e221b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99cae8459a00c122c3c2618b17c2e64176628829","tid":39763,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T18:27:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34cb0b37b252ebb3571f3e2a217b70faddedfd3c","tid":39763,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T18:27:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i4/vWaZz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi4%2FvWaZz.jpg&h=8aa8d791&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33fb07a81164398086a843d8c510939fd1b5d977","tid":39763,"uid":27210,"l